title: Deanna Cook // 72
description:
In 2012, a 32-year-old Dallas, Texas woman was found murdered in her own bathtub. She had called 911 during her death, but the call wasn't described as an emergency by the 911 operator, so her life wasn't saved. When her family found her dead in her home days later, and they knew exactly who killed her. This is the murder of Deanna Cook.
